title: New: Jeremiah Jae – Fame (Prod. By Ras G)
content:
After Jeremiah Jae announced that he would be releasing a track a day for the next 10 days, this just 5 days ago, I concluded that bringing you guys new music would be pretty easy, at least for the next 10 days. In reality I forgot about the whole damn thing. On a brighter note, the series of tracks has sucked me once again, in the form of this mist laden, spaced as hell jam in collaboration with Ras G, a producer who receives nowhere near as much attention as he deserves.

With a few more tracks on the horizon from this Black Jungle Radio series, head over to Jae’s soundcloud to soak them up.
